550
00:50:32.520 --> 00:50:35.590
♫ <i> Happiness is you</i>♫

551
00:50:35.590 --> 00:50:37.460
성덕미, 파이팅!

552
00:50:37.460 --> 00:50:41.480
♫ <i> Happiness is you</i>♫

553
00:50:47.200 --> 00:50:50.200
